title: Apple Jam Packs *Complete*
description:
This is the complete collection, all 6 Apple Jam Packs, no installation required just unzip and drop the folders directly into the "Apple" folder, which is located here... HD > Library > Audio > Apple Loops > Apple 

Bonus Loops SFX from iLife and SFX from FCP

Final Cut Pro Sound Effects
iLife Sound Effects
Jam Pack 1
Jam Pack Remix Tools
Jam Pack Rhythm Section
Jam Pack Symphony Orchestra
Jam Pack Voices
Jam Pack World Music

You should delete or overwrite the folders that are already there which will be the five Jam Packs not including World Music.

All the instrument library files that were on the original Jam Pack install disks are not needed as they are supplied free with the latest GB 10.2
